# Pass 0114 Ledger: Multi-Domain Constrained Optimization Suite

Date: 2026-07-01

## Objective

Extend the YouTube-critical optimization lane from one constrained-MPC receipt
into a reusable multi-domain constrained optimization suite. The point is not to
solve warehouse operations, robotics quality control, safety-critical
allocation, or quantitative finance. The point is to force one receipt schema to
carry domain source leads, exact constraints, feasible witnesses, objectives,
negative fixtures, market/source anchors, and Crucible verdicts.

