## YouTube Binding

The YouTube corpus continues to act as market and architecture pressure, not as
proof. Pass 0114 uses three source clusters from pass 0102:

- `enterprise_quantum_optimization`
- `quantitative_finance_laws`
- `agi_risk_scenarios`

The suite preserves the pass 0102 boundary:

```text
valid_video_count = 19
transcript_receipt_count = 19
raw_transcript_included = false
source_policy = YouTube videos are treated as critical source leads.
```

